{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-listing-index-tsx","path":"/blog/","result":{"pageContext":{"articles":[{"banner":{"alt":"","caption":"","src":null},"body":"<p>Tistory, Velog를 거쳐 Github 블로그로 오게 되었다.</p>\n<p>Gatsby로 개발된 테마를 사용하였으며 개설하는 방법을 작성하였다.</p>\n<br/>\n<h1>1. Gatsby를 선택한 이유</h1>\n<p>Github 블로그를 만들 때 주로 Jekyll와 Gatsby를 사용한다.</p>\n<p>Jekyll은 Rudy 언어로, Gatsby는 React를 기반으로 만들어졌다.</p>\n<p>평소에 React에 관심이 있었기 때문에 Gatsby를 선택하게 되었다.</p>\n<br/>\n<h1>2. Gatsby 및 테마 설치하기</h1>\n<p>Gatsby CLI를 설치해야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install -g gatsby-cli</code></pre></div>\n<p>원하는 테마를 골라 새 Gatsby 사이트를 만든다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// gatsby new [이름] [테마 URL]\ngatsby new portfolio-minimal https://github.com/konstantinmuenster/gatsby-starter-portfolio-minimal-theme</code></pre></div>\n<p>설치 도중 아래와 같은 오류가 발생한다면 참고할 수 있다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>⚠️ gyp verb check python checking for Python executable \"python2\" in the PATH</p>\n<p>원인 : Nodejs 설치 시 파이썬 등 필수 요소가 자동적으로 설치되어야 하는데 실패하여 Python이 설치되지 않았음.</p>\n<p>해결 방법 : default 경로인 C:\\Python27에 Python 2.7을 설치한다.</p>\n<p>⚠️ gyp err! stack error: c:\\windows\\microsoft.net\\framewaork\\v4.0.30319\\msbuild.exe failed with exit code: 1</p>\n<p>원인 : node-sass와 sass-loader 버전이 충돌하였음.</p>\n<p>해결 방법 :</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>npm uninstall node-sass</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>npm install node-sass 혹은 yarn add node-sass</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>프로젝트 내의 node_modules 폴더, yarn.lock, package-lock.json 삭제</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>yarn install 혹은 npm install 재설치</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\n<h1>3. Gatsby 실행하기</h1>\n<p>gatsby develop를 통해 실행할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">cd portfolio-minimal\ngatsby develop\n# open localhost:8000</code></pre></div>\n<br/>\n<h1>4. Github Pages를 통해 배포하기</h1>\n<p>Gatsby 테마를 GitHub 페이지에 올리기 위해 gh-pages라는 패키지를 설치해야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install gh-pages --save-dev</code></pre></div>\n<p>설치한 후 package.json에 설정을 추가해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"deploy\": \"gatsby build &amp;&amp; gh-pages -d public\" // 추가\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>npm run deploy를 통해 Github Pages에 배포할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>좀 기다린 후에 Published 라는 메시지를 받았다면 배포가 완료된 것이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm run deploy</code></pre></div>\n<p>마지막으로 GitHub 페이지가 작동하려면 Repository Source Branch를 변경해야 한다.</p>\n<p>GitHub의 Repository 설정에서 배포 할 Branch(여기서는 gh-pages)를 선택한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.909090909090914%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/c9b55/image.webp 165w,\n/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/f2908/image.webp 330w,\n/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/cc661/image.webp 660w,\n/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/a66df/image.webp 990w,\n/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/d33d4/image.webp 1320w,\n/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/36ae5/image.webp 1496w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/04c57/image.png 165w,\n/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/d9ecf/image.png 330w,\n/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/1f083/image.png 660w,\n/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/7a3d6/image.png 990w,\n/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/78958/image.png 1320w,\n/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/e4ee8/image.png 1496w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/e92384e52b85a66521c3877eb1a5bc5a/1f083/image.png\"\n            alt=\"image\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>5. Google Analytics 연결하여 방문자 수 구하기</h1>\n<p>블로그를 시작하면 방문자 수를 확인하고 싶다.</p>\n<p>이럴땐 구글에서 제공하는 Google Analytics를 이용하여 방문자 수를 구할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>Gatsby에서 제공하는 플러그인 gatsby-plugin-google-gtag 을 설치해준다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>⚠️ gatsby-plugin-google-analytics도 있지만 더 이상 지원하지 않는다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install gatsby-plugin-google-gtag</code></pre></div>\n<p>그 다음 gatsby-config.js 파일에 설정을 추가해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">resolve</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">gatsby-plugin-google-gtag</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">options</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// You can add multiple tracking ids and a pageview event will be fired for all of them.</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">trackingIds</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n          <span class=\"token string\">\"G-XXXXXXXXX\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Google Analytics / GA</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>여기서 GA-TRACKING_ID은 Google Analytics에서 설정한 스트림 측정 ID 값이다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 27.272727272727277%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/c9b55/image2.webp 165w,\n/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/f2908/image2.webp 330w,\n/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/cc661/image2.webp 660w,\n/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/a66df/image2.webp 990w,\n/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/d33d4/image2.webp 1320w,\n/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/3e240/image2.webp 4392w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/04c57/image2.png 165w,\n/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/d9ecf/image2.png 330w,\n/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/1f083/image2.png 660w,\n/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/7a3d6/image2.png 990w,\n/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/78958/image2.png 1320w,\n/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/bff81/image2.png 4392w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/8e389a28ae7c0c3f18edc7a1af9532a1/1f083/image2.png\"\n            alt=\"image\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>여기까지 설정이 끝나면 Google Analytics 홈에서 결과를 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>참고</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/konstantinmuenster/gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal/tree/main/gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal#using-the-content-directory\">Gatsby Theme Portfolio Minimal</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://kmkmi.github.io/Gatsby%20%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%20%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%20%EB%8F%84%EC%A4%91%20%EB%A7%8C%EB%82%9C%20%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC/\">Gatsby 블로그 적용 도중 만난 에러</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://codingapple.com/forums/topic/%EC%B5%9C%EC%8B%A0%EB%B2%84%EC%A0%84-%EA%B9%94%EC%95%98%EC%9D%84%EC%8B%9C-%EC%9D%B4%EB%9F%B0-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC%EA%B0%80-%EB%96%A0%EC%9A%94/\">최신버전 깔았을시 이런 에러가 떠요</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.zoomkoding.com/gatsby-github-blog/\">Gatsby 테마로 GitHub Blog 만들기</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","categories":["Gatsby"],"date":"January 29, 2023","description":"Gatsby를 이용해 간단한게 만드는 나만의 블로그","id":"82108ddd-e127-5633-8689-384c90dc682d","keywords":["Gatsby"],"slug":"/start-gatsby-blog/","title":"Gatsby로 블로그 만들기","readingTime":{"text":"4 min read"}}]}},"staticQueryHashes":["1094019748","1764120992","2442753764","2572006233","3525841079","460736852","513457919","540466502","597217301"],"slicesMap":{}}